You are very powerful when you learn to choose this or that, rather than just choosing to say, "Okay."

(1) Give them information.
(2) Say, "You could do this or that."
(3) Then they're uncomfortable and ask, "What would you do?"

(1) Give them information.
(2) Tell them what to do.
(3) They feel like they made a decision when they say, "Okay."
I try to give people info to make their own decisions. Often, I find that they prefer to be told what to do.
